room_title: Escape room "Dark Side of the Moon" by Houston Escape Room in Houston
room_description: Follow the story of Janet Monday in this new episode. This time, a colleague of hers was put in a coma after one of the experiments at PharmaCo went terribly wrong. Janet has been trying to create an antidote and left her research to you. You have 60 minutes to retrieve the antidote and escape before the PharmaCo's task force arrives.
